                                                </div> <br />

                                                <div class="text-uppercase">
                                                    <p><h5><b>GENERAL ADMISSION REQUIREMENTS</b></h5></p>
                                                </div>

                                                <div>
                                                    <h6><b>(I) UTME</b></h6>
                                                    <p class="mb-0 mt-3">Admission is open to candidates who wrote the <b>2022 Unified Tertiary Matriculation Examination (UTME).</b></p>
                                                    <ol type="a">
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Applicants are to complete the online Application Form by visiting Edo State University, Uzairue website at: www.edouniversity.edu.ng</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>All applicants are required to meet the Departmental minimum entry requirement of five (5) credit passes in relevant subjects including English Language and Mathematics at GCE O' Level/SSCE, NECO, NABTEB or their equivalents at not more than two sittings. However, for Medicine and Surgery (MB;BS), the five credits (including Mathematics and English) must be obtained at one sitting only.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Candidates awaiting results in (b) above may also apply.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>All applicants will be required to go through Edo State University Uzairue (Formerly Edo University Iyamho) Screening Exercise.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Candidates who wrote the 2022 UTME but did not choose Edo State University Uzairue as First Choice can apply by changing their choice of University/Course of Study to Edo State University as follows:</li></p>
                                                        <ul>
                                                            <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                            <li>Apply for Change of Institution through JAMB</li></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                            <li>Complete the Edo State University Uzairue Online Application Form</p></li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                    </ol>
                                                </div>

                                                <div>
                                                    <h6><b>(II) DIRECT ENTRY</b></h6>
                                                    <p class="mb-0 mt-3">All Direct Entry candidates are required to purchase and process the 2022 JAMB Direct Entry Form. Edo State University Uzairue accepts the following for Direct Entry Admission into 200 Level:</b></p>
                                                    <ol type="a">
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>A minimum of Merit pass in NCE, Credit in OND/HND or a University degree in relevant discipline.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Candidates with two Advanced Level passes or its equivalent in relevant subjects.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>The Interim Joint Matriculation Board (IJMB), Joint Universities Preliminary Examination Board (JUPEB) or Cambridge moderated School of Basic Studies at acceptable grade levels.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>In addition to a University degree/NCE/ND/HND/IJMB/JUPEB or two Advanced Level papers specified by each Faculty or Programme, candidates must also satisfy the O' level requirements.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Any other qualification as approved by the University Senate.</li></p>

                                                    </ol>
                                                </div>


                                                <div>
                                                    <h6><b>(III) TRANSFER CANDIDATES</b></h6>
                                                    <p class="mb-0 mt-3">Candidates will be allowed to transfer from other NUC accredited Universities to Edo State University Uzairue provided they meet the following conditions:</b></p>
                                                    <ol type="a">
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Purchase and complete the prescribed Edo State University Inter-University Transfer application Form online.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Pass interview/Screening conducted by Edo State University Uzairue.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Hold the minimum entry requirements for admission into Edo State University Uzairue.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Hold JAMB admission letter to your current University.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Ensure that the transcript of their academic records are received in the Admissions Office of Edo State University Uzairue.</li></p>
                                                        <p class="mb-0 mt-3">
                                                        <li>Have a C.G.P.A. of not less than 1.5</li></p>
                                                    </ol>
                                                </div>

                                                <div>
                                                    <h6><b>APPLICATION FEE</b></h6>
                                                    <p class="mb-0 mt-3">UTME/DE and Transfer Candidates are expected to pay the sum of Two Thousand Naira (N2,000) for Post UTME/ DE Application fee and Sixty Thousand Naira (N60,000) Transfer Application fee respectively.</b></p>
